d and that and - and we would have maybe have a nice tea and that and - sometimes - I would say - can the girl in my class come to the wee tea ma? Yes. Is she in your class? I said, oh yes. She would come and Lizzie would get one out of her class. But not
 a lot. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Did you have something special to eat?
