e used to order it. And we would have fruit and stuff and all the rest of it, and have a lovely tea, and then - if - your birthday as I say, she would maybe buy you something nice. I got a locket one time, I don't know, I've lost it, it had - with a chain
 on it. Then my aunts would give us something you know, beads or something or a - a little handbag. That's what we had, you know.
