Yes, we had - dances - occasionally when we were in the Children of Mary, certain nights a week. And concerts. But we never performed in the - concerts. We didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Did the church have any sort of club for people who didn't drink?
