t us, aye, the teachers were very - in those days very - strict with us if - if you said a - a wrong word they contradicted you and made it say - say it right and used to say, now - that is not the proper way to speak. And they would - they would check yo
u
 - would check you for it, but - we spoke properly, 'cos - we - our father, with him being Irish although, he was Irish, if we spoked - one word in Scotch here - if it wasn't the right word he would contradict us, and make us say the proper word and corre
ct us and my mother the same. Although - we were born all the - the - we were born in Scotland here, but off - Irish descent, they both con}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12853325\charrsid7227600 
tradicted us if we said - a wor}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 d that we shouldn't have said.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 At your first school, the one you went to when you 
were five if you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
Well we got checked but - I can't ever say - really - that I got the cane off of the - headmaster in those days, but of course - the - he only kept the cane for the 
- the teacher didn't use the cane, it was just a see small strap they had, but I never got the strap, never in my life at the school. But I've often been checked from the - she would just used to say now - no, no, and put her hand up you know and - and th
a
t. But - but for - although - do you see, my father was very intelligent, and sometimes at night if we were doing homework - in the house and - if we were - hesitated my father would look, and he would say, what is it? What's the word? Well, we couldnae p
r
onounce it, he would pronounce it, he used to say, spell it out. And we'd spell it out to him and then he would say it and then we would - know then that it was the right word to - have, and then put it down in the homework book you see. And that was - my
 father helped us a lot - with - with our education you know. Aye, but my - my mother - of course - my mother was a great }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12853325\charrsid7227600 sewer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600  in her day with her hands, you know, and she would sit and sew a lot and then my father - maybe read the evening paper and he wou
ld put it down, and if we were doing our homework - and werenae right sure of anything, he - he would help us with it. That was how we come on in school. Look at me, I left the school at thirteen as I say, I'd one year more to go, and - they were make - g
oing to make me go to the education - not the - church school I mean. So my father had to sit a board for me to get off, and - there were a priest there from the chapel, he had to be there with my father, so as I could get off school. Aye. I had to.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 So your parents took a great interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Oh aye, we did, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Did they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
No, they never needed to go up to the teachers any time for - anything - for us, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Was it common for parents to go up to the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
Well, not always you know. Never I can say that - the children in they days right enough - there were some poor wee souls I can go back to when they wore clogs, in they day, some had their barefeet, even in the snow, and still - they never 
had education clothes. No. We never had them. No. We never got them. No. We didn't need them because - we had aunts that were - even apart from having our aunts being dressmakers, my mother would have seen that - we were - we would have had whatever she w
as going to put on us. Aye, we had - parents like that. They watched us, and in every way they could. Every way. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 The education clothes were provided by the school were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Aye. The - the ones that got them right enough, but we never got th
em and they were very few people that got them. I think they had to be in very - great circumstances before they would get them. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Were girls punished the same as boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Oh aye. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 For what sort of offences would the children get punish
ed, for being cheeky or being late?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
Well, the teachers - the teachers - if they had an excuse with a line with them, if their parents were ill or that - they never got a strap or anything. But - if they stayed off on their own account - the teachers 
wouldn't - slap them with the belt, they never got it - she used to say, now you'll stand with your - your back to - to the wall there and you'll remain there 'til I tell you - to come round again to the seat. And some - the teachers in they days - were v
ery very good teachers. They were good. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Did all the other children come from similar sorts of homes as your own?

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Aye, I think some - the biggest part of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 There were one or two poor ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Aye, I think the biggest part of them
. I could never say - any of the children - then with - with me in the different classes - I can't remem - mind any of them - ever getting a severe punishment off their parents, any of them. No, I don't think they did. And they were all I think - I think 
t
hey were like myself, they - they were all allowed - in - if they did get out for an hour to play they were - the - the - that would be out there but they would have to go in cot when they were told, and that was it. But here - they're out here to ten and
 
eleven o'clock at night here. Aye. And I'll say that, oh my, the changed days. In more ways than one to what I was - getting - brought up - very very strict and - I used to look at my father and say, oh my, my father's terrible. I cold never make him out 
h
e was so strict. My mother - she was - my mother wasn't easy going but - she never intervened - if - if we - got - we - got checked one time, maybe for - maybe - we never disobeyed in our life right enough, not that I can mind it, but - my mother wouldn't
 
intervene and say to my father, she didn't do it or - or that's right or it's wrong, she never spoke, my father'd just say, now - and that was it, the hand went up and that was it. But I never could say that we got the belt in our life, none of us. Not on
e of us. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
Did the teachers single out any of the children for treatment differently from any of the other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Oh no, I don't think so. No, the teachers were pretty good. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 There were no favourites?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 No, they hadnae - they 
treated each - one that were in their classes all the same. All the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
No. No. We all played - out in the playground and one never hurt the other and - there was no fighting. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Not that I know of, no. I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Not even the very poor children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
I don't think so. There were poor children there like - but they were nice and clean you know. In they days we - they had a frock on, and it was wore with like a pinafore on the top you know, that they were all - kept clean you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Did you to another school after this one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
No, was the - just to the one school. St Colombus. That was at - we left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 How old were you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Would you have stayed longer if you could have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
Well I'd have been kept probably on to fourteen only on account of my mother dying. I had to be taken off school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Would you have liked to have stayed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
Aye, well - at - at - I - I wouldn't have - maybe perhaps - learnt more because - I was - my father as I tell you taught us - from we were so high to hold a pencil and write, you know. He taught us a lot and - and do it the right way and it was a wron
g word and he would tell us it, that's wrong and he would write it and then we - we'd have to do it over again. He helped us a lot. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15823640 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 Did you ever go to any evening classes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15232123 KS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 No, we didn't. My sister Lizzie did but - she 
