{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Rowan Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} had - they had it outside but the toilet out there you know. But it was a beautiful kept stair, it was an open }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12853325\charrsid7227600 banister}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1067686\charrsid7227600 
