h the Orange Bands and all that came out but - my parents never interfered with nothing like that, they never - no time for it. Well I'm the same. No, no, I never mingle not - I wouldnae cause trouble because - I'll say no, no, they didn't do it so theref
ore I'm no doing it, neither I do, no, I wouldnae mingle with it, you know what I mean. Go out I mean like as you say and - and maybe cause - trouble, no, no, they didn't do it either. No.
