Oh I did it, aye, but I didnae get the wage for it, oh no. No. So anyway - that - that was part of my work you see, with him, you see. 'Cos - when she got her breakfast Margaret she stayed in as I tell y
ou, she come down for her breakfast, but then she didn't come on for the lunches. I was with the chef. She come down for her lunch and went off to her bedroom again in the hotel. And then come down at five o'clock again with -
